    Use RDFParserBuilder.canonicalValues and one of RDFParserBuilder.langTagCanonical() and RDFParserBuilder.langTagLowerCase()

    This operation is equivalent to 

       this.canonicalValues(flag);
    if ( flag )
        this.langTagCanonical();
    else
        this.langTagAsGiven();
    return this;
